summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 33832, entitled, "An Ordinance authorizing and directing the levy and collection of a new assessment or reassessment to pay the cost and expense of and for the improvement of Fourth Avenue South between Seattle Boulevard and the south margin of Holgate Street, and Connecticut Street between Seattle Boulevard and the west margin of Oriental Avenue, as specified and provided for in Ordinance No. 18008, and providing payment therefor," approved October 27, 1914.
